Skills.Name: Beware the Ripples
Skills.Description: Inflicts <code=400,param=256><color=#3398f1>Weakness</color> ({0}% of skill user's ATK) on single enemy for 10s. Lowers DMG Inflicted for all enemies by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 15s. Further lowers DEF by <color=red>{2}%</color> for 15s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts Weakness on single enemy. Lowers DMG Inflicted and DEF of all enemies
